'''Bada Baldiiq''' ({{lang-en|Baltic Sea}}; {{lang-ar|بحر البلطيق}}) waxay ku taal woqooyiga [[yurub]] waxaa ku hareeraysan [[jasiirad]]<nowiki/>a wadamada loo yaqaan Scandinavianka<ref>[[:en:Scandinavia|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scandinavia]]</ref>, yurubta dhexe, yurubta woqooyi, yurubta bari, jasiiradaha [[denmark]], waxay ku xirantahay biyo mareenka Øresund<ref>[[:en:Øresund|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%98resund]]</ref>, iyo [[suunka wayn]] (Great Belt<ref>[[:en:Great_Belt|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Belt]]</ref>) iyo [[suunka yar]] (Little Belt<ref>[[:en:Little_Belt|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Little_Belt]]</ref>), waa bad biyaheedu yihiin (Brackish water<ref>[[:en:Brackish_water|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brackish_water]]</ref>) biyaha badda ka cusbo yar wabigana ka aan gaarayn oo ka cusbo badan, badaan ayaa [[badda cad]] uga darsanta marin biyoodka kanaalka bada cad<ref>[[:en:White_Sea–Baltic_Canal|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/White_Sea%E2%80%93Baltic_Canal]]</ref>, bada woqooyina waxay uga darsantaa kanaalka kiel ama (The Kiel Canal<ref>[[:en:Kiel_Canal|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kiel_Canal]]</ref>)

[[Dowladaha baldiiqa]] magacooda ayaa ka soo jeeda bada baldiiqa owaxayna kala yihiin ([[Latfiya]], [[estoniya]], iyo [[Lithuaniya]])

== Magaca ==
Qofkii ugu horeeyay ee magacaan u bixiya ayaa ahaa Adam of Bremen<ref>[[:en:Gesta_Hammaburgensis_ecclesiae_pontificum|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gesta_Hammaburgensis_ecclesiae_pontificum]]</ref> oo [[jarmalka]] u dhashay isagoo ugu magac daray [[jasiirad]] ku dhex taal isla bada bildiiqa laguna magacaabo Baltia<ref>[[:en:Baltia|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baltia]]</ref>, waana magac loo bixiyay waqtigii roomaanka.

bada ayaa magacyo badan le hadba sida ay tahay luuqada cida tilmaamaysa:
* [[Luuqadaha jermanka]]<ref>[[:en:German_language|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_language]]</ref> markii [[ingiriiska]] laga reebo waxay u yaqaanaan Bada bari tusaale ahaan [[jarmalka]] waxaa looga yaqaan: (Ostsee)
* [[finland]] iyo [[estoniya]] ayaa u yaqaan bada galbeed (Läänemeri).
* luuqadaha [[roomaansi]]<nowiki/>ga, sulaafiga, baldiiqa, [[ingiriiska]] iyo [[laatiinka]] ku magacaaba bada baldiiqa tusaale laatiinka: (Mare Balticum).

== Juqraafiga ==
Bada baldiiqa ayaa aad u qoto gaaban, moolka ugu dhexaadsan waa ku dhawaad 55 mitir, badaan ayaa la sheegaa inay tahay meesha ugu wayn [[aduunka]] ee ay ku jiraan isku milanka biyaha macaan iyo kuwa dhanaan, dhirikeedu waa ku dhawaad 1610 km, balarkeeduna waa 193 km, moolkeeda ugu dheer waa 460 m wuxuuna u dhawyahay wadanka [[iswiidhan]], baaxadeeda aya u eg 377 kun oo isku wareeg, xeebteeda ayaa dhirirsan wax ka badan 8000 km.

